<section class="section section--compact" id="advisory-tax-planning-disclosure">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="disclosure">
      <strong>TechBrot is not a CPA or tax firm and does not provide tax advice, prepare returns, or create tax strategies &mdash; your CPA or EA does that work.</strong> Tax planning and any tax strategy decision belong to your licensed tax professional. What we do is the bookkeeping that makes planning possible: we keep your books accurate and current, surface the numbers your CPA needs, and coordinate with your CPA throughout the year so planning isn&rsquo;t a year-end scramble. Nothing on this page is tax advice, and we never present a tax strategy as our recommendation. We are also an independent firm &mdash; not Intuit, and not Intuit&rsquo;s official support. QuickBooks and Intuit are registered trademarks of Intuit Inc.
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

