      <p>The clean split is the whole point. Your CPA or EA owns the tax planning: the strategy, the entity and compensation decisions, the estimated-payment figures, the advice. A Certified QuickBooks ProAdvisor at TechBrot owns the books behind it &mdash; accurate, reconciled, current numbers, projected income tracked through the year, and the data points worth a CPA conversation surfaced early rather than discovered in April. We coordinate with your CPA on a schedule so the numbers they need arrive organized and on time. We don&rsquo;t give tax advice, we don&rsquo;t create tax strategies, and we never present a planning decision as ours. Independent firm &mdash; not a CPA or tax-preparation firm, and not Intuit.</p>
